channel.description:
[table][tr][td]Hello Moparscape[/td][/tr][/table] My name's Gabriel, I run and host this server at the moment. I'm still debating wether or not i should release this publicly (Only Moparscape). Wanted to come here release some pictures, get some responses, and feedback.
Title says most of the information here's the rest: [b]Revision:[/b] [i]634 Cache[/i] [b]Base:[/b] [i]PI[/i]
[b]Server Security Folder:[/b]
[b]*[ CHAT-LOGS ][/b] -- [ Usernames ]
[b]*[ COMMAND-LOGS ][/b] -- [ Usernames ]
[b]*[ IP-ADDRESSES ][/b] - [ Usernames ]
[b]*[ TRADE-LOGS ] -- [ ITEMS-GIVEN ][/b] --- [ Usernames ]
[b]-- [ ITEMS-RECEIVED ][/b] --- [ Usernames ]
[b]*[ USER-PUNISHMENT ][/b] -- [ Banned ] --- [ Usernames ]
-- [ IPBanned ] --- [ IP Addresses ]
-- [ IPMuted ] --- [ IP Addresses ]
-- [ Muted ] --- [ Usernames ]
[b]*[ USER-REPORTS ][/b] -- [ Reports ] --- [ Usernames ]
[i][b]Newly added 100% Dicing + Clan chat output!! Dice Selection 2 Pages just official.[/b][/i]
[b][First Page][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/Dice1.png[/img]
[b][Second Page][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/Dice2.png[/img]
[b][Private Test Rolling][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/Dice3.png[/img]
[b][Clan-Chat Rolling][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/Dice4.png[/img]
[i][b]100% Vote4Cash Reward Adding[/b] [/i][i][IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/Voting.png[/img][/i]
[i][b]City Teleports[/b] [/i][i][IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/NewTeleportInterface.png[/img] [/i]
[b]Some of the Mini-Games:[/b]
[b]92% Castle Wars[/b] [i][pic soon][/i]
[b]95% Duel Arena[/b] [i][pic soon][/i]
[b]100% TzHaar/Jad (Just 1 wave for fire cape)[/b] [i][pic soon][/i]
[b]85% Fight Pits (Needs corrected respawning)[/b] [i][pic soon][/i]
[b]100% Barrows[/b] [i][pic soon][/i]
[b]100% Warriors Guild[/b] [i][pic soon][/i]
[b]Combat Features:[/b] [i]90% RS Hitsplats + Correct opacity + fading. Random max hit display. Venge + Venge Other with hit division formula. 100% Poisoning.[/i]
[b]Rotating Character Equipment Screen[/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/EquipmentScreen.png[/img]
[b](Random Login Screen Picture)[/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/LOGIN.png[/img]
[b]Weapon Specials at 100%:[/b] [i]Korasi Hand Cannon Staff Of Light Dragon Claws All PVP Weapons (Vesta etc) Dragon Mace Magic Shortbow Dark Bow All Dragon Weapons![/i]
[b]Skill Features:[/b] [i]98% Woodcutting Update for Woodcutting: now 98% right axes + emotes nests etc. 100% Crafting 100% Fishing (Redone) 100% Prayer (+ Randoms) 100% Rune Crafting (+ Pouches) 95% Agility (Horrible Area) 100% Thieving (+ Random Hits) 100% Farming (Redone) 95% Cooking (Redone) 85% Fetching 100% Herb-lore 100% Mining 95% Smithing (Needs Interface Work) 95% Fire Making Update for Fire Making: Now completed 95% still needs clipping done.[/i]
[b]Known Glitches:[/b]Interface Overlay Clicking Mishaps. Duel Arena 50-50% Chance of not respawning correctly..
[b]Quest Tab/Settings Pictures:[/b]
[b][First Menu][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/Quest.png[/img]
[b][Second Menu][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/SettingsTab-1.png[/img]
[b]Available Bosses:[/b]
[b]King Black Dragon (DFS)[/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/RangeHitSplat.png[/img]
[b]Corporal Beast (Spirit Shields)[/b] [i][pic soon][/i]
[b]Bork & Tarn (Korasi + Hand Cannon)[/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/Bork.png[/img]
[b]Dagannoth Kings (Misc Dragon + 3rd)[/b] [i][pic soon][/i]
[b]And to wrap up the picture, here are the new hit splats added in.[/b]
[b][Melee][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/MeleeHitSplat.png[/img]
[b][Range][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/RangeHitSplat.png[/img]
[b][Mage][/b] [IMG]http://i951.photobucket.com/albums/ad355/rspsman/2GO/MagicHitSplat.png[/img]

[b]Second Update Logs With Date Attached:[/b] [code]LAST UPDATED: 7/06/2011 -Here is a list of the In-Game updates recently added- -If you are looking for the most recently updated, look towards the bottom-
